          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "OpenAI and Anthropic automatically cache the KV (key-value) tensors for the attention computation over a prompt prefix. If the next request starts with the same prefix, the prefill computation is skipped and you pay a discounted rate on those tokens. This is entirely server-side \u2014 no changes to your code are required."
          }
        ]
      },
